profile_positions.description:
As Operations Director for Datora Telecom, I was responsible for two Network Operation Centers (one of them related to fixed telephony operations and the other one related to mobile operations) and the Onboarding Team. That involves ANATEL STFC, SCM and SMP interconnections management, as well as network monitoring, network configuration and troubleshooting of technical issues. As a Director, I had under my responsibility: 

- To manage a Team of around 40 people;
- Strategic Planning;
- Budget definition and control;
- Project Management;
- Quality Management.
